{"tid":81299,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"正確的喝水方式  補充水分 含1分鐘再下肚","createTime":"2017-01-15T08:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-15T15:56:02.000Z","uid":37554,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7cee6740dde5a5d00ff8223cfadd93bdb365ab5c","tid":81299,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:17:09.000Z","msg":"晚餐後少喝水較健康<br />\n<br />\n天氣熱易口渴而補充更多水分，但其實喝水也是一門學問，台大家醫科醫師姚建安表示，人一日約需攝取2000~3000c.c.水分，喝水時，先含在口中1分鐘，身體較易吸收，並建議晚餐前喝完一日所需水分，避免頻尿而干擾睡眠，因許多人熟睡時會不自覺憋尿，長期易造成女性尿道感染，男性則可能發生攝護腺疾病；中醫師莊雅惠也建議日落後少喝水，以免引發腹瀉。報導╱張雅淳 攝影╱黃天佑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/twapple_sub/640pix/20100724/MN05/MN05_001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2Ftwapple_sub%2F640pix%2F20100724%2FMN05%2FMN05_001.jpg&h=73f447fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正確的喝水方式，才能讓身體真正吸收水分。"},{"pid":"7397978ec743b6069bbe470a640ae0dd8d6d9298","tid":81299,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:18:26.000Z","msg":"張圖做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76d2acfe6bbab39999acbb7cfa3cce4461ca1dd","tid":81299,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7027117d62211075ecd59cd367e3bf14c657facb","tid":81299,"uid":26019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8669ba557ff0578aaee0e8031232480fdf4a12","tid":81299,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T08:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee9b50959fc10ffd9827b4ccefa5fdfe99a771a7","tid":8